  "prompt": "Which are the companies that hire freshers in Analytics (R programming)?",
  "response": "There are several companies that hire freshers for analytics roles, particularly those that involve R programming. While the specific hiring landscape can change frequently, here are some types of companies and examples where freshers might find opportunities in analytics:\n\n1. **Consulting Firms**:\n   - **Deloitte**\n   - **Accenture**\n   - **McKinsey & Company**\n   - **Boston Consulting Group (BCG)**\n\n2. **Technology Companies**:\n   - **IBM**\n   - **Microsoft**\n   - **Google**\n   - **Amazon**\n\n3. **Financial Services**:\n   - **Goldman Sachs**\n   - **JP Morgan Chase**\n   - **Morgan Stanley**\n   - **American Express**\n\n4. **Healthcare and Pharma**:\n   - **Pfizer**\n   - **Johnson & Johnson**\n   - **Novartis**\n   - **Cigna**\n\n5. **Retail and E-commerce**:\n   - **Walmart**\n   - **Target**\n   - **Flipkart**\n   - **Zalando**\n\n6. **Startups**:\n   - Many analytics-focused startups look for fresh talent. Examples include companies like **Zebra Medical Vision**, **DataRobot**, and various analytics consulting firms.\n\n7. **Research and Academia**:\n   - Universities and research institutions often hire fresh graduates for research assistant positions.\n\n8. **Government and Non-profit Organizations**:\n   - Organizations involved in public health, social research, and economic analysis may seek analysts with R skills.\n\n### Tips for Freshers:\n- **Internships**: Gaining experience through internships can significantly improve your chances of landing a full-time position.\n- **Networking**: Attend industry meetups, webinars, and workshops to connect with professionals in the field.\n- **Online Job Portals**: Use platforms like LinkedIn, Glassdoor, Indeed, and Naukri to search for entry-level positions.\n- **Skill Development**: Keep improving your skills in R and other analytics-related tools (like SQL, Python, Tableau, etc.) to increase your employability.\n\n### Conclusion:\nThe demand for analytics professionals is growing, and many companies are open to hiring freshers with the right skills. Keep an eye on job openings and apply to those that match your interests and qualifications.",
